title: 2011 West Coast Fever season
text: The 2011 West Coast Fever season was the fourth season that the <a href="West%20Coast%20Fever">West Coast Fever</a> contested the <a href="ANZ%20Championship">ANZ Championship</a>, and the fifteenth year of the franchise's competitive history. In 2011, the Fever were coached by Jane Searle, in her third year as head coach. The 2011 season saw little change in the team's struggling history in the ANZ Championship, finishing in ninth place.
